title: Minimap Component
source:
[[include component:minimap-base
   latitude={$latitude}|
   longitude={$longitude}|
   width={$width}|width=200px|
   height={$height}|height=450px|
   color={$color}|color=red|
   caption={$caption}|caption= |
   float={$float}|float=right|
   zoom={$zoom}|zoom=8|
   latviewoffset={$latviewoffset}|latviewoffset=0|
   lonviewoffset={$lonviewoffset}|lonviewoffset=0|
   visualstyle={$visualstyle}|visualstyle=toner|
   crosshair={$crosshair}|crosshair=true
]]
